rComments: Il présente la matière de façon très méthodique, ce qui a bien fonctionné pour moi.  Pas de surprise, on applique la méthode et on a la réponse.
Well organized, methodical presentation.  Very helpful when you go to see him.  Nice guy, good teacher.

Best teacher in the department.  Although he doesn't speak loud and is very timid/shy/reserved, his teaching method is effective.  His classes are organized and structured.  Hard assignments, but they help you learn.  If you have questions (and if you can find his office), he's always available to help you and is open to comments.
A good prof with a good attitude; howevr, the relevancy of the course with my carrer is the question.  As long as you attend all of the quizes and tutorials, you should do fine.
